title: DNSK - The TrapXoid Sessions - Volume 1.0
description:
I made this Trap DJ Mix in a total state of mental harmony one sunny afternoon at home in my apartment in the small town I live in. When I finished up I realized that this mix is something special, something special indeed, so before I even uploaded it to my sites, I just sat down and started to create an audiovisual video to it.

In any case,

Enjoy!
